title: Are We Garbage? (feat. Joe List, Nate Bargatze, H. Foley & Kevin Ryan)
description: DJ Lou updates the gang on his love life. Joe List tells the guys about proposing to his wife and he deep love of Pearl Jam. Jay and Dan welcome Nate Bargatze and discuss dating. Dan, Jay and comedians Kevin Ryan and H. Foley of the "Are You Garbage" Podcast look pack at playing with their “guys”.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
